parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission slipping and jerking can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle shudders
vibrates
or jerks when shifting gears
especially between 20-40 mph. The transmission slips or hesitates when accelerating
and the vehicle may stall or lose power.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission failure and lockup can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: The transmission locks up or fails to engage
causing the vehicle to stall or lose power. The vehicle may hesitate or jerk when shifting gears
and the transmission may slip or hesitate when accelerating.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission shudder and vibration can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle shudders or vibrates when shifting gears
especially between 20-40 mph. The transmission may slip or hesitate when accelerating
and the vehicle may stall or lose power.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission failure to engage can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: The transmission fails to engage when shifting gears
causing the vehicle to hesitate or stall. The vehicle may not move when shifted into gear
and the transmission may slip or hesitate when accelerating.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The activation of the airbag warning light can indicate a potential airbag malfunction, which can lead to accidents or injuries if the airbag fails to deploy or deploys unnecessarily.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is illuminated on the dashboard
and the vehicle may have a history of airbag recalls or repairs.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag to deploy in the event of a crash can lead to serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The airbag fails to deploy in a crash
and the vehicle may have a history of airbag recalls or repairs.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The Takata airbag recall issues can lead to the failure of the airbag to deploy or deploy unnecessarily, which can cause serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle has a Takata airbag recall notice
and the repair parts are unavailable or delayed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the airbag sensor can lead to the failure of the airbag to deploy or deploy unnecessarily, which can cause serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The airbag sensor is faulty
and the vehicle may have a history of airbag recalls or repairs.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the dealer to properly diagnose and repair airbag issues can lead to the failure of the airbag to deploy or deploy unnecessarily, which can cause serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The dealer fails to diagnose or repair airbag issues
or uses incorrect parts for the repair.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the driver's seat mounting bracket can cause the seat to become unstable, rock back and forth, or even detach from the vehicle floor, which can lead to accidents or injuries, especially in the event of sudden braking or a crash.
symptoms: The driver's seat feels loose or unstable
the seat rocks back and forth
the seat tilts backward
the seat makes a loud popping or snapping sound
the seat becomes detached from the vehicle floor.
